Just wanted to let all of you know about a new book on Solr. Administrating Solr by Surendra Mohan. The book is a practical, hands-on guide that will provide readers with step-by-step exercises to help them administrate, monitor, and optimize Solr using Drupal and its associated scripts. It gives good knowledge of Solr and also covers a small part of drools. You can check it out here, http://bit.ly/1cNmREG</description>
